  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "On the corrupted world of Garm, Madox of the Thousand Sons has stolen the Spear of Russ and means to use it as the key to a ritual gate for Magnus the Red. Ragnar Blackmane, Strybjorn and Sven race into the old Space Wolves and Thousand Sons hatred, fighting through sorcery, relic-worship and the weight of their Chapter's history. Ragnar's choice at the portal costs the Wolves their sacred spear but saves them from a worse return, marking his passage from Blood Claw toward Grey Hunter. A brutal chapter-myth of sacrifice and inherited war.",
